  "title": "Operations Manager",
  "description": "<p>Responsibilities:</p>\n<p>1. Supervise and coordinate assigned work; conduct daily pre-operation meeting with staffs on duty</p>\n<p>2. Conduct On-the-Job Training (OJT) to employees including the proper and safe manner of carrying out routine operations</p>\n<p>3. Ensure all daily operations are carried out as per schedule</p>\n<p>4. Attend to complaints and ensure customers' satisfaction</p>\n<p>5. Any other duties assigned by Superiors and Clients</p>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<p>1. 6-Day Work Week (8am-7pm)</p>\n<p>2. Able to work OT including weekends and public holidays.</p>\n<p>3. Able to work outdoors in islandwide locations and able to go to multiple locations daily.</p>\n<p>4. Excellent customer service skills and able to interact well with clients</p>\n<p>5. At least 5 years experience in similar role</p>",
